://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr98v06T.jpg&h=3e553ae1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母我笑左"},{"pid":"20cb793af9223ba3f355bae3467e48d064c504ce","tid":239711,"uid":41112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T03:18:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r98v06T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr98v06T.jpg&h=3e553ae1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母我笑左</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befe32bf84fb80b5471d0869caad6ef246a8582a","tid":239711,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T03:18:17.000Z","msg":"比人話講嘢Mean, 不過唔覺得自己仆街<br />\n會覺得Mean多數係因為講中咗，然後拎咗嚟玩諷刺<br />\n見過唔少比人話得講嘢Mean嘅，其實講嘅全部都係事實，好多時都係一針見血<br />\n其實就係因為一嘢見血，其他人先會覺得你講嘢Mean姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a8f2a98bf69bf4674503ab0ebfca026587f261","tid":239711,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T03:23:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黑色幽默<br />\n<br />\n9up</blockquote><br />\n應該算係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但黑色幽默係咪唔應該存在</blockquote><br />\n黑色幽默其實係有少少深度，少少想去講某事/人有咩唔啱唔合理<br />\n<br />\n所以取笑就唔包既，純粹滿足大家睇人仆街最開心既心理姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2873d696946e0e3d5b2ba65c10fb435d192630c6","tid":239711,"uid":61985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T03:23:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比人話講嘢Mean, 不過唔覺得自己仆街<br />\n會覺得Mean多數係因為講中咗，然後拎咗嚟玩諷刺<br />\n見過唔少比人話得講嘢Mean嘅，其實講嘅全部都係事實，好多時都係一針見血<br />\n其實就係因為一嘢見血，其他人先會覺得你講嘢Mean姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個重點都唔係講唔講中<br />\n佢話你mean 係因為你講嘢太過直接 會令到人地唔舒服 唔係咩都講得 而你竟然拎講中咗嚟打飛機"},{"pid":"a8a8cfbb36dd0bd0205916fbe35d9c64b99dcfb7","tid":239711,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T03:28:02.000Z","msg":"睇場合啦，無傷大雅就無乜所謂，<br />\n但hurt到人就無意思啦<br />\n同埋睇下取笑對象係咪真抵比人笑先，<br />\nmean spirit嘅笑話同間接bully其實都唔係爭好多"},{"pid":"3d518aa7d66d3674d3d827f476766c21df7da9a7","tid":239711,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T03:33:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比人話講嘢Mean, 不過唔覺得自己仆街<br />\n會覺得Mean多數係因為講中咗，然後拎咗嚟玩諷刺<br />\n見過唔少比人話得講嘢Mean嘅，其實講嘅全部都係事實，好多時都係一針見血<br />\n其實就係因為一嘢見血，其他人先會覺得你講嘢Mean姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個重點都唔係講唔講中<br />\n佢話你mean 係因為你講嘢太過直接 會令到人地唔舒服 唔係咩都講得 而你竟然拎講中咗嚟打飛機</blockquote><br />\n唔講中咪唔會直接，有咩打唔打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩件事有關係啵師兄"},{"pid":"61abdffb22ec41d92ace3ba333c3f3dc6d5e78a4","tid":239711,"uid":62294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T03:35:40.000Z","msg":"我諗緊仆唔仆街或者係咪無傷大雅係咪應該Depends on自己心中嘅尺 而每個人都有唔同嘅尺 社會嘅道德標準就係平均嘅呢把尺<br />\n例如我把尺應該係：<br />\n有張笑黑人細路嘅圖我覺得Ok<br />\n有張笑死咗嘅黑人細路我覺得Over<br />\n<br />\n咁即係冇正唔正確之分 都係睇過唔過到自己嗰關?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff3b5d1f2e35255566ba107cb227174fb96d36c","tid":239711,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T03:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>黑色幽默<br />\n<br />\n9up</blockquote><br />\n應該算係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但黑色幽默係咪唔應該存在</blockquote><br />\n點色幽默唔mean架喎<br />\n甚至你完全唔知幽緊默<br />\n<br />\n例《一念無明》<br />\n你想唔想死？想死就要入返青山架啦喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諷刺社會嘅荒謬唔Mean<br />\n但講完笑完會自己覺得好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢啲就係黑色幽默<br />\n<br />\n講野mean以前叫毒舌腹黑<br />\n近牌叫返mean"},{"pid":"1b50efcb696f6b6091447fc16a79b7fb4e2c3267","tid":239711,"uid":61050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T04:13:07.000Z","msg":"mean jer大哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}